Subject: drm/i915/guc: Convert mapping table to iosys_map
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: c723b8ee3864bdf41cc560da958b7ef7f6138f0b
